g retirement.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his upcoming retirement\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Physically it's just too tough now.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the injuries have added up and like I said they have not been insignificant.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injuries\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to play forever.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love this sport.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's given me so much, taught me loads of lessons over the years that I can use for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"loads\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"lessons\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to stop so it is hard.'\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In hispost-match press conference, Murray appeared to leave the door open to continuing in doubles, only specifically ruling out singles when asked if he could be tempted to make a U-turn to play Wimbledon one last time next year in 2025.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hispost-match press conference\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"doubles\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"a U\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Before what happened in Miami (a nasty ankle injury) I was starting to play good tennis,' Murray added.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2709, \"end\": 2714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"score\": 0.9546739551585822, \"rank\": 0.04743189486462045, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.345634456647623e-35, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nasty ankle injury\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"good tennis\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of all the memories Andy Murray has given us, one stands above the rest.On 7 July 2013, in living rooms and town squares across the country, we celebrated the end of a 77-year-wait\\u2026pic.twitter.com/j23kLcwkRE 'At Queens I got through the first round.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2810, \"end\": 2821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the memories\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"7 July\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"living rooms\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"town squares\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"a 77-year-wait\\u2026pic.twitter.com/j23kLcwkRE\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"Queens\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3008}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can still win matches at this level.\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with the physical issues around the hip, I was still able to compete at the highest level.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the physical issues\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the hip\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Not as consistently as I would have liked.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Certainly not having the results I would have wanted.\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But yeah, I can definitely still win matches here or on the grass once I am recovered from the back injury.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"the grass\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"the back injury\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not want to do that now.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I could do it, but I have no plans to play singles again.'\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no plans\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on June 27, Andy Murray said: 'I know that there is more important things in the world than how I finish playing my last tennis match or where I finished playing my last tennis match.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3502}, {\"ngram\": \"more important things\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"my last tennis match\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"my last tennis match\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But because of what I put into the sport over the last however many years, I would at least like to go out playing a proper match where I am at least competitive, not what happened at Queen's (where his back injury forced a mid-match retirementand subsequent surgeryruled him out of Wimbledon singles).\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"the last however many years\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3754}, {\"ngram\": \"a proper match\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3810}, {\"ngram\": \"Queen\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3870}, {\"ngram\": \"his back injury\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3895}, {\"ngram\": \"a mid-match retirementand\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon singles\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So I can not say for sure that if I wasn't able to play at Wimbledon, and I did not recover in time to play at the Olympics that I would not consider trying to play another tournament somewhere.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4085}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"another tournament\", \"from\": 4151, \"to\": 4169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I am able to play at Wimbledon and if I am able to play at the Olympics, that's most likely going to be it.'\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4218}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray has said retiring at Wimbledon or the Paris Olympics would \\\"be fitting\\\" and he is unlikely to play at the US Open or Davis Cup later this year.He spoke to the BBC about his future planshttps://t.co/JJbKS1m5nlpic.twitter.com/NUKQLpdVca Speaking to theBBCin June 2024, Andy Murray said: 'I do not think [I will play at the 2024 US Open or the Davis Cup].\", \"fro