 \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4748, \"to\": 4764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have had amazing experiences and memories from Wimbledon, but also being part of British Olympics teams.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4895, \"end\": 4902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.908347066462221, \"rank\": 0.05389825487022023, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing experiences\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4842}, {\"ngram\": \"memories\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 4855}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 4861, \"to\": 4870}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To get a chance to compete at a fifth one is a reason to stay motivated and continue playing.'\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 5015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 4936}, {\"ngram\": \"a reason\", \"from\": 4966, \"to\": 4974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after he lost to Tomas Machac at the Miami Open in March, Andy Murray said: '[It is] the last match that I am going play here, which is sad, because I love it here.\", \"from\": 5017, \"to\": 5190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5084, \"end\": 5095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.442892702357007e-66, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tomas Machac\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5055}, {\"ngram\": \"the Miami Open\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 5077, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"the last match\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5125}]}